<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="182" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,767,1118]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">
<collectorName box="[136,159,768,794]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">In</collectorName>
the protologue only 
<collectorName box="[383,596,767,793]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Herbarium Munich</collectorName>
(M) and 
<collectorName box="[694,927,767,793]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Herbarium Zuccarini</collectorName>
are mentioned (
<bibRefCitation author="Martius, C. F. P. V." box="[1101,1253,767,793]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="98 - 102" refId="ref7849" refString="Martius, C. F. P. V. (1826) XXXII Luhea Willd. Nova genera et species plantarum: quas in itinere per Brasiliam MDCCCXVII-MDCCCXX 1 (4): 98 - 102." type="journal article" year="1826">Martius 1826</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." pageId="2" pageNumber="182" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 325). 
<bibRefCitation author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[348,505,803,830]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry box="[348,421,803,829]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated 
<typeStatus box="[627,725,803,829]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">holotype</typeStatus>
(M), but without having seen it or specifying its identification number. 
<collectorName box="[237,392,839,865]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Consequently</collectorName>
, this designation must be corrected as 
<typeStatus box="[841,944,839,865]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">lectotype</typeStatus>
and as a first-step typification (Art. 9.17 of the ICN). 
<collectorName box="[253,302,876,902]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Two</collectorName>
specimens of 
<emphasis box="[471,608,876,901]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">
<collectorName box="[471,560,876,901]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Martius</collectorName>
s.n.
</emphasis>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[627,775,875,901]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="divaricata">
<emphasis box="[627,775,875,901]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. divaricata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) are in 
<collectorName box="[869,1024,875,902]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Herbarium M</collectorName>
based on data found on the label. 
<collectorName box="[1428,1451,876,902]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">In</collectorName>
accordance with 
<collectorName box="[326,382,912,938]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Arts.</collectorName>
9.3 and 9.4 of the ICN, we herein designate specimen (M0210165) as a second-step 
<typeStatus box="[1349,1452,911,937]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">lectotype</typeStatus>
by choosing the best-preserved specimen congruent with the protologue’s description. 
<collectorName box="[1134,1226,947,973]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Another</collectorName>
<specimenCount box="[1235,1418,947,973]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" type="generic">three specimens</specimenCount>
of 
<emphasis box="[136,273,984,1009]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Martius s.n.</emphasis>
(M0210175, M0210179, M0210180) are also found in M; however, no evidence, including label data, indicates that they are duplicates of the 
<typeStatus box="[579,682,1019,1045]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">lectotype</typeStatus>
herein designated. The exsiccate (M0210176) is only a reproduction of Figure 63 from Martius’ work. Based on 
<bibRefCitation author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[660,819,1055,1082]" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry box="[660,733,1055,1081]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
and the present study, the application of the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="182" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="divaricata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="182">L. divaricata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confirmed as an accepted species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
